Rdio,is,an,online,music,radio,service,that,provides,access,to,millions,of,songs,in,almost,every,genre,Users,can,play,songs,whenever,they,want,as,many,times,as,they,want,or,they,can,listen,to,stations,that,combine,their,current,favorites,with,similar,unheard,songs,The,Rdio,oEmbed,API,allows,developers,to,retrieve,the,embed,code,for,an,album,track,or,playlist,using,either,the,resource,s,full,or,shortened,URL